    {
      "id": "c697588b-73e5-4e80-9fc4-9bf1e99f092d",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Moreover, the authors show that it is possible to use a week-wise granularity to make such predictions, with the model being abel to achieve 90% accuracy whithin the first 10 weeks (out of 38). ",
